paragraphs.text:
%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW tweets
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "s3a://dsci6007.kinesis.data/output/tweets"
)

%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW hashtags
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "s3://dsci6007.kinesis.data/output/hashtags"
)

%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW users
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "s3a://dsci6007.kinesis.data/output/users"
)

%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW top_hash AS
SELECT hashtag, COUNT(1) AS freq FROM hashtags GROUP BY hashtag ORDER BY freq DESC LIMIT 10

%sql 
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW first_event AS
SELECT hashtag, freq, MIN(timestamp_ms) AS timestamp_ms
FROM top_hash 
JOIN hashtags USING (hashtag)
JOIN tweets USING (id)
GROUP BY hashtag, freq

%sql
SELECT DISTINCT hashtag, freq, screen_name, first_event.timestamp_ms, tweets.created_at 
FROM first_event 
JOIN hashtags USING (hashtag)
JOIN tweets ON hashtags.id = tweets.id AND first_event.timestamp_ms = tweets.timestamp_ms
JOIN users ON user_id  = users.id
ORDER BY first_event.timestamp_ms
